        <Parent_String>cranes (equipment) [300022331], transferring construction equipment [300167975], construction equipment [300022242], equipment by process [300024659], equipment [300122241], Tools and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300022238], Furnishings and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300264551], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
